      <item>
        <title>Error deploying to hosting</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Johan]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>You should upload the source files to the server and run the build command on the server itself, instead of uploading the build files to the server.</p>
<p>And you should make sure you have enough permissions to build and run the required commands on the server.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/error-deploying-to-hosting/5046/2">Read full topic</a></p>
